        'Document time, reading, and actions taken.'],
    it:['Red threshold (68%) exceeded — check sensor for condensation.',
        'If accurate: immediate facilities alert required.',
        'Export event log CSV for DHF records.']},
  of:{lv:'red',title:'🔴 NODE OFFLINE',
    cl:['Ganglion node not transmitting. Environmental monitoring unavailable.',
        'Notify IT to investigate immediately.',
        'Do not rely on last known reading for compliance decisions.'],
    it:['Node stopped transmitting. Check power and indicator LED.',
        'For AETH Hub: confirm USB connection and bridge script is running.',
        'For mesh nodes: check LoRa range — may have been moved or powered off.']},
  // Vitals next steps
  vhr:{lv:'red',title:'🚨 HIGH HEART RATE — >120 BPM',
    cl:['Heart rate exceeds normal range (60–100 BPM).',
        'Assess subject immediately — verify electrode contact and rule out artifact.',
        'If confirmed tachycardia, follow facility cardiac emergency protocol.',
        'Document time, BPM reading, and actions taken.'],
    it:['BPM >120 threshold exceeded. Verify finger placement on MAX30102 sensor.',
